[02:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'problem. AI video does not remember your characters unless you give it something to remember. The model has no loyalty to your book. It doesn\'t know what your heroine looks like. Like I said, from'

[03:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'the first page to the 300th page, every generation is a fresh guess. Most people Most people try to solve this with a better prompt. They even feed the prompt'

[03:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'into an AI to get it to enhance the prompt. That helps. It helps a little, but it doesn\'t hold. What actually holds is a system, a ladder of control that'

[03:25] [scene:talk]
